data.description: **SELLER OFFERING 10K FOR YOU TO USE ANY WAY!**Welcome to this beautifully updated 4 bedroom 2 bath home located in Crestview, SOUTH of I-10. The core of this home comprises a spacious living room with an opening to the kitchen, a formal dining room, and a flex room that features magnificent built-ins, making this room the perfect office or reading nook. The bedrooms are generously sized, including the primary suite with an en-suite bathroom. That bathroom includes a soaking tub, double vanities, a separate shower, and double closets. The outdoor space is a true retreat, with an in-ground gunite saltwater pool under a screened enclosure. Additionally, a handy storage shed is available for your outdoor needs. This home is conveniently located near Northview Park & Disc Golf Course. NO HOA. Roof: 2019. HVAC: 2019. Floors: 2020. Paint: 2020. New Septic Drain Field: 2020. Pool Resurfaced: 2020. Yard Building: 2021. Take the chance to experience the property firsthand; schedule your showing today! *Sellers are Licensed Real Estate Professionals
